pt.iade.cCollector.models

Class Collection

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.iade.cCollector.models.Collection

  • public class Collection
extends java.lang.Object
    This class models a collection for two purposes: 1. To model the logged users collections. 2. To allow a user to choose a new collection.
